{
  "stem": "6257.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And push-- and then-- and from my point of view, I-- somebody got up, and-- and-- to-- to go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I sat down in their place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were people I knew who had been quite nice me, sort of in this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when this woman came back, and kind of looked at me, I was probably sitting in her-- sort of began to shout that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She obviously knew all this time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But hadn't-- you know-- and-- so they [INAUDIBLE] and a lot of people were suddenly [? became ?] sort of saying almost-- something about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in fact, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in fact, you know, people [INAUDIBLE] sort of quieting down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember that maybe I shouldn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I sort of [INAUDIBLE] under stress and strain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I-- well I think [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zerimba ?] was my surname.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was supposed to be the-- some cousin from Pomerania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that part of Poland was under some different German occupation, some different system.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there wasn't much contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So people couldn't check up so easily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the underground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Perhaps [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- so we-- so some people, the young-- young people, were sort of put-- taken somewhere to-- to-- and then I remember people wanting to be my-- be with me because I was the child.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you-- they had a child, they would probably not be sent to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few people volunteering to be my mommy or daddy, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But we were put on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Families, mainly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- the train-- I don't know where the train was going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It stopped somewhere for minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
